description: "Map of the South Peninsula of Celebes (Sulawesi), spread over four sheets. It features crops (alang-alang, coffee, rice, sugarcane), routes (roads, rivers, postal routes), mountains, forests and settlements. The Gowa Regency is left blank."
title: "Kaart van Zuid Celebes met uitzondering van het Rijk Gowa / in steendruk gebracht aan de Topographische Inrichting te 's-Gravenhage."
